# 🤖 TerminusAI - Your Terminal AI Companion

[![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/version-1.0.0-blue.svg)](https://github.com/testlolplz/TerminusAI)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-green.svg)](LICENSE)
[![Termux](https://img.shields.io/badge/Termux-Compatible-orange.svg)](https://termux.com)
[![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.7+-yellow.svg)](https://python.org)

**TerminusAI** is a powerful, feature-rich AI assistant for Termux that brings the power of Large Language Models directly to your Android terminal. **100% FREE** - No credit card required!

## ✨ Features

| Category | Features |
|----------|----------|
| **🤖 AI Chat** | Powered by OpenRouter's free tier (Gemini, Llama, Qwen, DeepSeek) |
| **🎨 Customization** | Create your own AI personalities with custom prompts |
| **💻 Code** | Execute Python code, syntax highlighting, code analysis |
| **🔍 Web** | Search the web, get news, fetch weather |
| **📁 Files** | Read, write, download, and manage files |
| **🔊 Voice** | Text-to-speech output for responses |
| **📝 Productivity** | Todo lists, reminders, password generator |
| **📱 Utilities** | QR codes, system info, storage stats |
| **💾 Backup** | Save/load chats, export to markdown, backup system |
| **🎮 Commands** | 25+ slash commands for everything |

## 📋 Requirements

- **Termux** (install from F-Droid, NOT Google Play)
- **Python 3.7+**
- **Internet connection**
- **OpenRouter API key** (free)

